trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> 類別的執行個體的集合。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart> within the collection represents an extensibility element added to a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>, and specifies the MIME type for a corresponding <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>.
trans-unit.target: 每個<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart>代表集合中的 擴充性項目加入至<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeMultipartRelatedBinding>，和指定的 MIME 型別對應<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>。

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關指定的 XML Web 服務通訊協定的詳細資訊，請參閱[ [ \<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 如需 Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL) 的詳細資訊，請參閱規格的http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/。

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 將指定的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> 加入至 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection" />，於指定索引位置。

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果已經在集合中的項目數等於集合的容量，容量加倍插入新項目之前，會自動重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `mimePart` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`參數等於<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>、`mimePart`參數加入至結尾<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection>。

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 向下移動以容納新項目插入點後的項目。

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePartCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，平均執行時間是成比例<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed `MimePart` move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 請依照下列所移除的項目`MimePart`向上移動以佔用空出的位置。
